  "remarks": "Irina Cherkasova is the Commissioner for Children’s Rights in the Rostov Region. In this role, she is one of the most involved persons in the illegal deportation of Ukrainian children to Russia and their adoption by Russian families. Irina Cherkasova’s actions violate the rights of Ukrainian children and infringe Ukraine’s law and administrative order.",
